channel.title: SquadScape - Do you have what it takes to join the SQUAD?!
channel.description:
[center]SquadScape, where your journey continues.
[img]http://squadscape.ipbhost.com/public/style_images/5_%5E21D28882D159105D6D282579903A399C564BAD7EB7A24668FC%5Epimgpsh_fullsize_distr.jpg[/img]
Download - [url=http://desktop.squadscape.com]desktop.squadscape.com[/url]
Forums - [url=http://forums.squadscape.com]forums.squadscape.com[/url]
A very recent server with an already die-hard community of helpful guys and girls at the center. We are striving to provide the best gaming experience an RSPS can offer, with new and exciting custom content and lots of different features to explore. We will give you your money's worth and your time well spent with the Squad.
We've got our own Skype group that anyone can be invited to through one of the pristine members of our community. There's always a person online to help and answer any question you may have. We're still in development and a lot is still up for change that you can be a part of; we're always open for your feedback and suggestions.
= Server owners = Slayer Task Mauled By U
= Features = Easy Barrows Pest Control Boss pets Custom NPCs Custom items Droprate rings Prestige system Canifis minigame Custom account security Custom client security ALL DUPES FIXED! 'Test your luck' items Qualified staff team Donor point store Zoom in/out on client Reward system for skilling Custom Slayer task system with points and shop Custom items Custom bosses Ability to recolour ANYTHING
= Screenshots =
Barrows [img]http://i.gyazo.com/c98a07545f62cd17a648b6ab55385ff6.png[/img]
Boss pets [img]http://i.gyazo.com/b8d16e223c85a4b15afd22176fa0c419.png[/img]
Skilling zone [img]http://i.gyazo.com/92c9c5e8a722b54b9b91bd78db487853.png[/img]
Extreme donor zone [img]http://i.gyazo.com/62cff05aca339e83633e2051707a700b.png[/img]
Canifis minigame [img]http://i.gyazo.com/edb8ef40b2f58ea82e3b6c0ac299a953.png[/img]
Slayer point store [img]http://i.gyazo.com/8aaadd296b8964462aeca565df1f258f.png[/img]
Donor points store [img]http://i.gyazo.com/32e5f55e0de99f3a2a574884b82118e8.png[/img]
Thank you for reading and we hope to see you soon!
